These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
4 different games are played: poker, snooker, mah-jongg, bridge
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, zinnia, aconite, poppy
1. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the left of the person who growsaconite##5
2. the person playing snooker is not the person who growsdaisy##6
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is not the person playing mah-jongg##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | snooker   | bridge    | poker    | mah-jongg |
| Sport      | poppy | daisy | aconite | zinnia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, december, june
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, superhero, documentary, spy
1. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
3. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
4. the person who's birthday is in september is not the person watching superhero movies##6
5. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
8. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | september  | december    | november | june    |
| Food       | spy | superhero | documentary  | western |

