.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, peach, grapes, onion
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, cricket, ice-hockey, badminton
1. the person eating onion is not the person who's sport is tennis##6
2. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person eating grapes##6
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
4. the person who's sport is cricket is the person eating orange##1
5. the person eating peach is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the person eating orange is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | onion       | peach  | orange  | grapes |
| Job        | ice-hockey | badminton | cricket | tennis  |

