.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, cycling, water-polo, badminton
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, crime, family, disaster
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5
3. the person watching disaster movies is not the person who's sport is cycling##6
4. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5
5. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
6. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | cycling | water-polo | badminton     | tennis |
| Transport   | crime     | family    | musical | disaster    |

