.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
City: berlin, prague, edinburgh, paris
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, rock-climbing, singing, photography
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
2. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5
3. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
4. the person traveling to prague is not the person who's hobby is photography##6
5. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person traveling to berlin##6
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | berlin        | paris | edinburgh | prague |
| Transport   | photography | writing | rock-climbing     | singing   |

