1. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is not the chaman-smoker##6
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the right of the vegafina-smoker##5
5. the person who growsbegonia is the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the bolivar-smoker##5
7. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the person who growsorchid##5
8. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the vegafina-smoker##5
9. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the vegafina-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | daffodil | begonia    | orchid  | balloon-flower   |
| Nationality   | game  | vegafina | chaman | bolivar |

