2. the owner of the goat is not the japanese##6
3. the german is the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
5. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
6. the japanese is the owner of the hamster##1
7. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | dutch | japanese     | colombian | german |
| Music-Genre   | goat | hamster | dog      | snake         |

