.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, chess, go, billiard
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, collecting, rock-climbing, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
5. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
7. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person playing go##5
8. the person playing chess is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | chess  | backgammon        | go      | billiard          |
| Job        | puzzles | collecting | board-games | rock-climbing |

