4. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is the victorian house##1
7. the cottage house is not the person watching disaster movies##6
8. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5

.:: Answer ::.
