3. the person driving the van is not the person watching superhero movies##6
4. the person watching adventure movies is between the person driving the airplane and the person watching superhero movies##2
5. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
6. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the motorbike and the person watching martial-arts movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | superhero | adventure    | martial-arts | drama |
| Music-Genre   | motorbike         | boat | airplane   | van     |

